      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Daniel Gierach of Ray White The Collective is an active agent across Brisbane's inner east and south, including Hamilton. He brings local market knowledge, a targeted buyer database and a proven track record of results across the inner south and east corridor. Call 0412 523 821 for a no-obligation appraisal."
